data.text: bandung is my home town..., the foods are incredible..., the people are ultra polite and nice..., but now bandung is also known for the heavy traffic...  whenever i go to bandung..., there's one place that i always visit..., rasa bakery..., presenting delicious cakes, pastry, ice cream, traditional foods, etc...  rasa bakery have been maintaining the consistent quality since i was little..., two thumbs up... btw, if you decided to visit this place, don't forget to try the home made ice cream, trully great....
